=This is an Instagram profile page. Extract the following data:

- Followers: Extract the total number of followers.
- Followed: Extract the total number of accounts followed by this profile.
- Reels: Provide a link to the Reels section of the profile.
- Stories: list all the stories, with its information, in the profile
- First Five Publications: Extract details of the first five posts, including:
  - Image or video description
  - Date of publication
  - Number of likes and comments if available
  - Any hashtags or mentions included in the post
